The accident, which took place near the Hendrina offramp, involved two light motor vehicles and a truck.  According to first respondents, the collision occurred at around 21:00 when the driver of the Corsa bakkie lost control of his vehicle and crashed into a truck and a Chevrolet bakkie.  Five people, including the father of the baby, were rushed to hospital for medical treatment but all three the drivers involved survived the incident. 